title: President Obama Surprises Joe Biden With Presidential Medal Of Freedom In Moving Ceremony
text: 11 diggs Twitter Politics In what was supposed to be a typical farewell event for vice-president Joe Biden, Barack Obama surprised his right hand man with the rare and coveted Presidential Medal Of Freedom. There wasn't a dry eye in the house. Advertisement
